  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>\"Strategy Meets Adorable Pixel Art! A New Roguelite Tower Defense Experience\"</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for Mayhem Maidens, a one-of-a-kind mix of tower defense and roguelite action! Take charge of a fiery team of five unique characters, fend off waves of enemies, and shape your adventure with clever strategy. With charming pixel art and endless customization options, every run feels fresh and exciting.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>\"Features\"</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Control 5 Characters Simultaneously:</strong><br>Why manage just one hero when you can lead five? Switch between characters on the fly, plug gaps in your defenses, and adapt to the chaos. It’s fast, it’s intense, and it’s an absolute blast!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299130/extras/3856890456d1f32b51ca2ce8fd53de05.poster.avif?t=1749009691\" width=800 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299130/extras/3856890456d1f32b51ca2ce8fd53de05.webm?t=1749009691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299130/extras/3856890456d1f32b51ca2ce8fd53de05.mp4?t=1749009691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Your Ultimate Squad:</strong><br>Experiment with wild skill combos, passive abilities, and creative builds. Whether you’re aiming for an unbreakable tank, a lightning-fast attacker, or a well-rounded dream team, the choice is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299130/extras/2c3fa1fa57c96d415d2cce955eeb2d21.poster.avif?t=1749009691\" width=800 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299130/extras/2c3fa1fa57c96d415d2cce955eeb2d21.webm?t=1749009691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299130/extras/2c3fa1fa57c96d415d2cce955eeb2d21.mp4?t=1749009691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Endless Replayability:</strong><br>Every run is different! Random skill unlocks and fresh challenges keep things exciting, and the satisfaction of crafting an overpowered squad never gets old. Crush your enemies in style and enjoy the rush of pure victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299130/extras/7b55ec98fe64e2aff002aeb68fb76e43.poster.avif?t=1749009691\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299130/extras/7b55ec98fe64e2aff002aeb68fb76e43.webm?t=1749009691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299130/extras/7b55ec98fe64e2aff002aeb68fb76e43.mp4?t=1749009691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Heartwarming Team Moments:</strong><br>Take a breather between battles to enjoy hilarious banter at the base. You’ll fall in love with the team's quirky personalities.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299130/extras/a9c45dbec28aa77adba02c9d2fb32732.poster.avif?t=1749009691\" width=800 height=226 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299130/extras/a9c45dbec28aa77adba02c9d2fb32732.webm?t=1749009691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299130/extras/a9c45dbec28aa77adba02c9d2fb32732.mp4?t=1749009691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>\"A Gorgeous Pixel World Full of Homura’s Charm!\"</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic pixel art with a fresh, modern twist — meet the girls who bring this world to life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each one is packed with personality and totally true to herself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They may look cute, but they’ve got minds of their own. Lead this wild crew to victory!</p>",
