"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299130/extras/a9c45dbec28aa77adba02c9d2fb32732.webm?t=1749009691\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299130/extras/a9c45dbec28aa77adba02c9d2fb32732.mp4?t=1749009691\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>\"A Gorgeous Pixel World Full of Homura’s Charm!\"</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic pixel art with a fresh, modern twist — meet the girls who bring this world to life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each one is packed with personality and totally true to herself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They may look cute, but they’ve got minds of their own. Lead this wild crew to victory!</p>",
